page.title: 13CHARLTON-HANK.ECOLOGY 3
page.content: {Flora.}Wood Anemone,Bluebell,Primrose, Celandine,Foxglove,Lady's Smock,Rose- bay,Willowherb,Enchanter's Nightshade, Herb Robert,Ragged Robin,Silverweed, Meadow Buttercup,Wood Dock,Red Campion, Stichwort,Dandelion,Trefoil Nettle, Chickweed,Grounsel,Shepherd's Purse, Speedwell,Fern,Thistles,Vetch and Cow Parsley are amongst the most common wild flowers found. Yellow Flags and Marsh Marigolds grow near ponds and ditches. Orchids,Fritillaries and Cowslips are also found. Most common grasses are also present:- Meadow Foxtail,False Brome,Crested Dog's Tail,Cock's Foot,Couch Grass, Yorkshire Fog,Wall Barley,Perennial Rye-Grass,Timothy,Common Bent,Sweet Vernal Grass,Tufted Hair Grass,Annual Meadow Grass, Wild Oat, False Oat grass and Soft Brome.
